title: Bicozin Syrup 100ml
details: Bicozin Syrup : Adults : 10 ml (2 teaspoonfuls) 2 to 3 times daily, Children : 10 ml (2 teaspoonfuls) 1 to 3 times daily, Infants:5 ml (1 teaspoonful) 1 to 2 times daily. Bicozin Tablet : Adults & Children over 30 kg : 1 to 2 tablets 2 to 3 times daily.

title: Rex Tablet 6mg+200mg+50mg
details: Indication:Reduces risks of cardiovascular diseases in human, reduces risks of cataract, combat infection and chronic diseases, trend toward decreased age-related degenerative changes, defense against infections.

title: Pregniforte
details: Pregniforte tablets are used for the treatment of female infertility caused by anovulation (lack of ovulation) or oligo ovulation (infrequent ovulation). The tablets contain a combination of Clomiphene Citrate and Metformin Hydrochloride, which work together to stimulate ovulation and improve fertility in women with these conditions.

title: Hemofix FZ Tablet 48mg+0.5mg+22.5mg
details: Description:Indicated by the treatment of iron, folic acid and zinc deficiency.

title: Zif-CI Capsule 50mg+0.50mg+61.80mg
details: Indication:Treatment and prophylaxis of Iron, Folic Acid and Zinc deficiency especially during pregnancy and lactation.
